     5→ * Real-Time Fairness & Drift Monitor
     6→ * ----------------------------------
     7→ * Listens to prediction events on a Kafka topic, maintains a sliding-window
     8→ * cache of model outputs, computes fairness metrics (statistical parity,
     9→ * equal opportunity) and basic concept-drift statistics (PSI), and emits
    10→ * alert events whenever thresholds are breached.
